            </ul>
                    <h4>UMLS Concepts <a href="/web/20180712204149/https://www.guideline.gov/help-and-about/search-browse/umls-concepts" class="what-is">(what is this?)</a></h4>
                <div class="field">
                    <h5 class="field-label">HCPCS</h5>
                    <div class="field-content">
<a href="/web/20180712204149/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_HCPCS_CUI=C1971399&amp;fLockTerm=Foot+pressure+off+loading%2fsupportive+device%2c+any+type%2c+each">Foot pressure off loading/supportive device, any type, each</a>
                    </div>
