 (713.5), <a href="/web/20180712204149/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0264049&amp;fLockTerm=Chronic+osteomyelitis%2c+ankle+and+foot">Chronic osteomyelitis, ankle and foot</a>
 (730.17), <a href="/web/20180712204149/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0375138&amp;fLockTerm=Diabetes+with+neurological+manifestations%2c+type+I+%5bjuvenile+type%5d%2c+not+stated+as+uncontrolled">Diabetes with neurological manifestations, type I [juvenile type], not stated as uncontrolled</a>
 (250.61), <a href="/web/20180712204149/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0375137&amp;fLockTerm=Diabetes+with+neurological+manifestations%2c+type+II+or+unspecified+type%2c+not+stated+as+uncontrolled">Diabetes with neurological manifestations, type II or unspecified type, not stated as uncontrolled</a>
 (250.60), <a href="/web/20180712204149/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0375142&amp;fLockTerm=Diabetes+with+peripheral+circulatory+disorders%2c+type+I+%5bjuvenile+type%5d%2c+not+stated+as+uncontrolled">Diabetes with peripheral circulatory disorders, type I [juvenile type], not stated as uncontrolled</a>
 (250.71), <a href="/web/20180712204149/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0375141&amp;fLockTerm=Diabetes+with+peripheral+circulatory+disorders%2c+type+II+or+unspecified+type%2c+not+stated+as+uncontrolled">Diabetes with peripheral circulatory disorders, type II or unspecified type, not stated as uncontrolled</a>
 (250.70), <a href="/web/20180712204149/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0017086&amp;fLockTerm=Gangrene">Gangrene</a>
