 (707.10), <a href="/web/20180712204149/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0264028&amp;fLockTerm=Unspecified+infection+of+bone%2c+lower+leg">Unspecified infection of bone, lower leg</a>
